|Kausalya]] as Bhavani<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n* [[Subhash Gupta]] as Rathore<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n* [[Jayasri]] as Vasundhara Dhar<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n\n==Season 1==\n\n===Episodes===\n{{Episode table |background=#0257AC |overall=  |title= |writer= |director=Soumik Sen |airdate=22 May 2019 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 1\n |Title = Let the game begin\n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |ShortSummary = \n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 2\n |Title = Preparations galore\n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |ShortSummary = \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 3\n |Title = The truth unfolds\n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |ShortSummary = \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 4\n |Title = The investigation begins\n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |ShortSummary = \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n }}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 5\n |Title = Drugs vs Politics\n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |ShortSummary = \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 6\n |Title = Boomerang \n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |ShortSummary = \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n |LineColor = 0257AC\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 7\n |Title = When everything goes wrong\n |DirectedBy = Raj Anantha\n |WrittenBy = Raj Anantha / Vishnu Manchu\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|df=yes|2020|2|11}}\n |Short